<section class="page-content">
  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <h2>Bringing FinTech Experience Together With the Next Generation of FinTech Companies</h2>
  <p>FintiQ was founded to provide <strong>specialized consultancy services</strong> for rapidly growing startups and scaled companies in the financial technologies sector.</p>
  <p>While the FinTech industry is growing at a breathtaking pace, the <strong>qualified human resources</strong> required for this growth are unfortunately not accessible at the same speed. However, there are <strong>highly experienced professionals</strong> who know the dynamics of the industry and have successfully executed numerous solutions in the market, still actively pursuing their careers.</p>
  <p>FintiQ aims to be a platform that <strong>brings together FinTech companies in need</strong> of such expertise with these valuable <strong>professional capacities</strong>.</p>
  <p>Founded by leaders who have served in <strong>senior executive positions</strong> in banking and financial institutions for many years, FintiQ also leverages its <strong>Advisory Board</strong>, composed of experts who continue their <strong>active professional careers</strong>, to deliver <strong>up-to-date, practical consultancy and guidance services</strong> to its clients.</p>
  <p>Our mission is to connect companies aiming for growth and sustainable success with <strong>professionals who have successfully applied their expertise in the field</strong>, and to <strong>be their companion on this journey</strong>.</p>
  <p>We offer <strong>end-to-end consultancy services</strong> in critical areas such as <strong>strategy, organization, technology, business development, and regulation</strong>, keeping pace with the industry's growth with our <strong>human capital and knowledge</strong>.</p>
</section>

